      </p>
      <p>
        <docTitle>Resolution adopted by the General Assembly on 17 December 2024</docTitle>
      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docProponent refersTo="#thirdCommittee">[on the report of the Third Committee (<inline name="originating document">A/79/459, para. 37</inline>)]</docProponent>
